As a special thank you and in celebration of #NFTNYC , everyone that requested access to the Lazy Lions VIP Dinner at #ROARNYC, whether you received an invite or not, will get access to claim a Lazy Comic NFT.

When does claiming begin?

Thursday 23rd June at 11am PT / 2pm ET  
ONLY trust links from the official Lazy Lions account.

How do you claim your NFT?

Via the dapp on the website. (Link posted tomorrow)

What if you had your Lazy NFTs in different wallets?

There will be a support process announced via Discord. We don’t want anyone who’s eligible to miss out.

How do you qualify for the claim?

You need to have all 3 Lazy NFTs(Lazy Lion, a Lazy Cub, and a Lazy Bungalow) in the same wallet when the snapshot was taken on the 22nd of June 2022.

You'll be able to check if you're eligible by connecting to the dApp. *Link posted tomorrow.*

How much does it cost?

The Lazy Comic is free to claim for eligible holders, you just pay GAS.

How can everyone else see the comic?

After the Exclusive Access period, all Lazy Lions NFT holders (Lazy Lions, Lazy Cubs, or Lazy Bungalows) will have access to view the comic for 2 weeks.

After that, only holders of the Lazy Comic NFT #1 will be able to view the comic.

A snapshot was taken on the 22nd of June (Block 15009538 at 09:00:15 PM +UTC) & all eligible holders will have 2 weeks to claim their Lazy Comic #1 NFT.

This 2 week period will also be the Early Access period for the comic book. Only holders of this NFT will be given access.

How can you get the comic?

The Lazy Comic #1 will be launched as an exclusive NFT which will be available to holders who own a complete set of Lazy NFTs (ie. a Lazy Lion, a Lazy Cub, and a Lazy Bungalow).

So, who’s Glitch?

Glitch is the Lazy Lions evil antagonist. You've gotta keep an eye on that guy... he's here to cause trouble
With the rise of Glitch, we wanted to tell you the backstory of how he came to be. And what better way to do that than a comic book?
